  "description": "Canine Morphus table (Nightbane RPG p. 97; Dark Designs p. 130). Wolves are most common, but dogs of all types, foxes, and other canines are possible. All canine characters instinctively get Tracking at 40% and Swimming at 50% in Morphus. In most cases, Disguise and Undercover Ops are impossible. Player selects specific canine species.",
